      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped potatoes</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong>,<strong> </strong>season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 20-25 min or until the potatoes are crisp – these are your <strong>mini</strong> <strong>roast potatoes</strong></p>",
