    {
      "instruction": "<p>Pat your <strong>basa</strong> <strong>fillet[s] </strong>dry with kitchen paper and add to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined tray, then sprinkle the <strong>cheesy breadcrumb mix</strong> evenly over the basa</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4 or more? Use 2 trays!</p><p>When the potatoes have 12-15 min left, put the tray[s] with the basa in the oven until the breadcrumbs are starting to turn golden and the basa is cooked through – this is your <strong>cheesy baked basa</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
